Class ReleaseId

    public class ReleaseId
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ReleaseId>
    A CodeBeamer release number contains of a sequence of major to minor release numbers, separated by '.'. E.g. "4.2.6", "5.2.1", "5.5"
